{"tid":577143,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇啲夢大家好深刻？又有冇人識解夢？","createTime":"2018-03-01T13:03:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-01T13:37:05.000Z","uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b5708b7b73b449f09d6b15acc81bd501ecf4a6f4","tid":577143,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T13:03:57.000Z","msg":"有個夢纏繞住我 已經過咗一個月 我重晚晚諗起呢個夢<br />\n<br />\n有晚發夢 全公司同事一齊公幹<br />\n點知去到機場我先發現自己忘記帶任何行李又無帶錢（全身得50蚊要捱幾日）<br />\n喺夢入面我好冇自信 驚大家睇我唔起<br />\n又驚比人知我冇帶錢<br />\n又驚比人知我嚟緊幾日冇衫換<br />\n夢入面好不容易過咗幾日<br />\n我每日都唔開心咁過<br />\n但又無工作夢境<br />\n到咗最後一日 上到旅遊巴去機場<br />\n我突然醒起漏咗件外套喺酒店房<br />\n夢境係之後要去D凍地方，但嗰刻衣衫單薄<br />\n但我好驚又唔敢講<br />\n唔敢叫司機返轉頭<br />\n但亦知唔拎返就以後拎唔返<br />\n我估起勇氣同一位同事講我漏咗件外套喺酒店<br />\n點知同事大聲講然後成班同事一齊聲討我<br />\n連老細都話我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後夢境就完咗<br />\n到呢刻諗起都眼濕濕有D唔開心"},{"pid":"b731d58e597e41bd8311dc9d725da0f7d7066baf","tid":577143,"uid":166320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T13:07:11.000Z","msg":"係咪有擔心過遇到咁既情境。"},{"pid":"8d0e6e0c3e0dff55bf55a6dfb1ba074a51fa8c22","tid":577143,"uid":8867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T13:16:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2ec032a870b44c94fd57234ae27755a618b7f652","tid":577143,"uid":171598,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T13:22:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/01/212050_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F01%2F212050_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=de97b88e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/01/212111_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F01%2F212111_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=98e6c7af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/01/212123_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F01%2F212123_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=ab836bdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n夢想過曬3個女神。啲夢仲記得。個時好緊張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c13f0d5b0c30caf371e896072328f087f2eda5dd","tid":577143,"uid":95508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T13:28:39.000Z","msg":"夢見自己推人落樓再諗方法毀屍滅跡 好撚真實"},{"pid":"51e247192031abcf1a7fbb12a7494a2dff1b0024","tid":577143,"uid":173949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T13:37:05.000Z","msg":"夢見自己見到有人肢解一個婆婆, 跟住我行行下望到周圍都係手手腳腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 重點係夢中既我見到呢D嘢好平靜"}]}